attributes.content: Everyone! Everybody! Would you look at that!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: Before this match began, who could’ve known that this fight—this standoff between the renowned Nearl family and the Plastic Knight—would’ve turned out like this?
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: Maria Nearl! The girl who inherited the Nearl name! Who could’ve seen this coming—!?
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: She’s completely cornered by Szewczyk! And she’s got no way to turn the tables!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: That won’t do! Nearl! Do you know how much money our audience has bet on you just because of your name?!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: Uh... Say that again? Oh, it’s not actually that much, going by where the the odds stand? Hey now, you should all have a little more faith in the girl! Isn’t her face worth something to you?!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: Ughh—!
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: I was expecting something on Zofia or the Radiant Knight’s level, but is this all you’ve got...?
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: What a let-down.
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: That’s the Roar Guards’ old war horse! He’s using the artificial environment and his speed to his advantage! The poor girl’s got nowhere to run!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: He stops! He shoots! And then he’s on the move again! This is his 'Plastic Rhythm'!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: (I-I can’t see his movements! Why? He’s not even as fast as Zofia—)
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: (He stopped! I’ve gotta block—!)
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: Too slow!
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: —Maria! To your left!
attributes.name: Zofia

attributes.content: What—Uhgh!
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: Szewczyk just hopped on the wall there and made a beautiful burst of shots. My god, if he landed those shots where he really wanted them, we’d have to cut the broadcast short! That was close!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: Even though he’s been hit a few times already, his armor is so tough, there’s absolutely no sign of damage at all! Yet he’s able to move around in it so quickly! Astounding!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: You see that, everyone? That’s the latest product from the Roar Guards! The Jack 2 Special High Performance Rubber Paste!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: This fantastic product can be yours today! But wait! We’re even handing out 5% off coupons at the front of the arena right now! Be sure not to miss this opportunity!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: So... That’s Nearl?
Hold on, is she really the Radiant Knight’s sister?
...What, are you disappointed?
Of course not... Why would I be disappointed by something like this? What about you?
Me? Well... Let’s keep watching a little longer. We paid good money for our tickets after all.
I hate the atmosphere here... and Mob never fails to get on my nerves.
I don’t understand how he manages to stir up the crowd when he commentates like that... And those advertisements... Is anyone actually running out to buy anything he’s advertising?
There’s probably a few.
After all, letting viewers put everything off their minds and go with the crowd is what these knight competitions do best, wouldn’t you agree?
Hey, take a look over there. In the front row. 'Whislash' Zofia.
Not just her. There’s more over there... Some lesser-known knights.
...We have about ten minutes left.
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: Looks like your luck hasn’t run out yet. If I didn’t have to drag this out, you would’ve begged me to spare your life long ago!
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: Nngh—!
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: Just surrender, kid.
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: You don’t know the rules here. The judges aren’t going to stop us until I have arrows sticking through all your arms and legs.
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: You don’t need to do this. Throw in the towel.
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: I-I can’t give up...!
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: Well, if you’ve already dug your heels in... You have her eyes, but, other than that, you’re nothing.
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: Very well... Let’s see how long you can keep this up.
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: Training is nothing like real combat.
attributes.name: Zofia

attributes.content: No one’s going to try to be polite and take you head-on.
attributes.name: Zofia

attributes.content: Besides, each contestant has her own equipment, weapon, and fighting style. On top of that, each battle takes place on different terrain, there are different traps and support equipment... Any one of which could influence the outcome.
attributes.name: Zofia

attributes.content: Gathering intel sounds really important...
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: That’s right, and that’s where the problem is. There is no way you can remember the weaknesses of each and every one of the knights in the Kazimierz Major, but most if not all of them have their eyes on you.
attributes.name: Zofia

attributes.content: Ohh...
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: There isn’t a one-size-fits-all solution when it comes to winning the competitions, but if we have to come up with something...
attributes.name: Zofia

attributes.content: Bring out the best in yourself—In other words, give it your all.
attributes.name: Zofia

attributes.content: So, you mean... you’ve got nothing?
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: Ow!
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: Observe and think. You don’t come up with solutions before you actually face the challenges.
attributes.name: Zofia

attributes.content: You need to analyze the situation within an extremely short amount of time and come up with the appropriate response. That’s not an easy thing to do.
attributes.name: Zofia

attributes.content: —To the left!
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: You got lucky there.
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: Ohh?! This is the first time Nearl has countered his attack—Nope, all she did was block his feint!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: The vote count hasn’t changed! Szewczyk still has the advantage, and an overwhelming one at that!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: Observe. Think.
Maria—
You are gifted with a pair of pegasian eyes.
(His knight armor—Jack 2?)
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: (The Roar Guards have thirteen different products, and none are called that—)
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: ...Waiting for me to strike? Fool!
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: Several arrows buzz past Maria, sending strands of hair fluttering in the air and leaving behind a trail of smoke and dust in the air.
(It enhances his mobility... No, there’s more to it than that... but this model...)
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: ...Let’s give it a try.
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: She’s charging! 'Plastic' Szewczyk has been toying with Nearl so far this entire match, but she’s finally charging him for the first time!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: She dodged the flames burning through the crevices and the artificial frost! She’s fast! Very fast—But Szewczyk is still not moving away! Is he going to fight her head on?!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: It’s suicide for an archer to fight a swordsman head on—
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: You won’t get away—!
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: I’m not going anywhere!
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: The two contestants clash. Arrows whiz past Maria as she endures the intense pain on her face, yet she does not attack.
She steps atop her opponent’s armor and flips into the air. Naturally, Szewczyk did not expect the confrontation to be this friendly—
The coldness he feels in his hand, the low roar, and the unnatural smoke wafting in the air—
What’s this? Would you believe it?! We aren’t just getting a knight match for our money today; we’ve got a circus show going on here!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: Maria has finally closed in on Szewczyk, but she hasn’t attacked even once! Is this her idea of a taunt?!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: ...It’s not that she’s not attacking; she can’t attack. If she didn’t dodge that, her left arm would’ve been crippled by now.
attributes.name: Zofia

attributes.content: Plastic’s trying to drag the fight on. He’s trying to get sponsorships by putting on a show... *sigh*.
attributes.name: Zofia

attributes.content: Maria...
attributes.name: Zofia

attributes.content: What... did you just do?
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: It’s getting a little hot in here, isn’t it... Mr. Szewczyk?
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: Haven’t the Roar Guards thought out the ventilation issues in that new armor you’re wearing?
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: ...That’s something for the craftsmen to worry about, not for two dueling knights to have a discussion over.
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: (High performance, lightweight... It’s obviously trying to replicate that high-end Victorian workmanship and the Originium skeletal reinforcement lining technology from Columbia...)
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: (They probably left out air vents because of some technical issues... No, maybe just aesthetics...)
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: (In that case... How much longer till it reaches its limits?)
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: (He moves and shoots, then repeats. I know his pattern, but I can’t match his speed.)
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: (Wait, no... He moves, then stops, and then he shoots... Hold on...?)
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: We had a little interlude just now, but both sides have regained their composure! They pulled away from each other, and we’re back on track—Hang on!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: Maria’s not hesitating at all! She took off right away and she’s trying to match Szewczyk’s speed! But! There’s still some difference between them!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: You don’t know when to give up, do you? Hasn't 'Whislash' taught you not to make chase when you have the lower hand in speed?
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: Szewczyk briskly stops and turns. In no time, he has already replaced his bowstring.
(Now!)
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: A flash! The stadium is suddenly filled with a blinding light—Let’s take this opportunity to look at all the advantages of Raythean’s latest sunglasses, part of its Pioneer line of apparel!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: (What? Advertisements? Who gives a crap when they’ve already thrown all that money on this?)
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: Nnn—!
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: She’s not attacking—What—
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: (He’s not attacking or moving! Again!)
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: —Hiyaah!
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: He blocked it! Szewczyk, a crossbowman, managed to block Maria’s attack without even breaking a sweat!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: Our Nascent Nearl, Maria, is running out of ideas!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: (I knew it!)
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: So the Arts were all just a fluke... Was there even a point to that? It was your last chance.
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: Mr. Szewczyk, how’s the automatic cooling system doing for you during combat?
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: Well, color me surprised... If you figured that out so quickly, maybe you should’ve been a mechanic, not a knight.
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: —Mr. Szewczyk, you’re a really strong knight. Your speed and techniques are impeccable.
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: Sadly, it looks like you chose to be a corporate product tester instead.
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: ...None of your business, and I suggest you stop underestimating the Roar Guards’ technological prowess.
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: —Is that so?
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: Ohh?! Maria’s willingly pulled herself back! What’s the meaning of this?! What were the two of them talking about?!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: I’m sure our audience is curious about that, too. I’ve always been an advocate for giving the knights mics—Who doesn’t want to listen in on our contestants trash-talking each other?!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: Well, the crowd’s getting all fired up again.
It seems like Maria Nearl figured something out.
Yeah, it looks like it. Well, no matter. Knights should spend more time thinking instead of always trying to brute force a win.
Cheap tricks...!
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: He stops! He shoots! Szewczyk’s starting his hunt again—Wait! Maria sidestepped the obstacles on the ground, and she’s dashing straight towards Szewczyk!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: Hmm?!
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: Szewczyk! Szewczyk’s not moving an inch! Is he going to take that hit straight on like last time?!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: *Warning sounds* Tsk! This stupid cooling system—!
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: Sorry about this!
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: Don’t get cocky!
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: Ugh?!
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: It’s suicide for an archer to fight a swordsman head on—I couldn’t have said it better myself!
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: (It hasn’t cooled down yet. I need to keep my distance!)
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: Out of the way!
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: Szewczyk—! Unbelievable! With just his crossbow and his bayonet, he blocked her flawlessly!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: Maria closes her eyes.
She has seen this technique countless times, and she has tried to imitate it just as many.
A move she has copied over and over and over.
Yeah... now I remember...
attributes.name: Zofia

attributes.content: That backhand thrust... It’s the same one that took Margaret to victory.
attributes.name: Zofia

attributes.content: You...
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: This is impossible...
attributes.name: Plastic Knight

attributes.content: Haghhh—
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: Th-That hurts...
attributes.name: Maria

attributes.content: —Wh-Who could’ve seen this coming?!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: Szewczyk still had the advantage just a second ago, but she knocked him cold in just one blow! There is no question. The winner is Maria!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: But how did she do that? Did we just witness a repeat of that miraculous final match?! Maria Nearl! Has she been hiding her true strength this whole time?!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: Well, well. She did  it.
...Let’s go.
Not gonna keep watching?
What’s there to watch? Better go home and fix up your weapon, don’t leave any weaknesses for your opponent to capitalize on.
Hahaha, you’re right about that. Wait up!
Maria... you really did it.
attributes.name: Zofia

attributes.content: ...Is this really a good thing?
attributes.name: Zofia

attributes.content: Mr. Mob.
(Hey! This stage’s for commentators! Get off!)
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: Shh... Quiet. Do not let the audience hear you... They cannot see me where I am standing, so relax.
I am just here to relay Mr. Pavel’s thoughts on the matter...
Pa... Y-You dare call him by name... What do you want?
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: It appears Szewczyk lost this match out of ineptitude. This has been a huge disappointment to the Roar Guards Company.
You mean...
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: Quiet now... There are some things that are best kept unsaid. I am sure you are aware what that means.
Now go, the audience is waiting.
Everyone—! Everyone!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: Going by the odds and votes, this has undoubtedly been a huge upset! This match is sure to be the talk of the town for days to come!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: An independent, untitled knight managed to defeat the Roar K.C.’s vanguard! It looks like Maria Nearl’s Originium Arts are a force to be reckoned with! She defeated the 'Plastic' Szewczyk, through pure skill!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: Was it because Szewczyk underestimated her opponent, a newbie? Was it their conversation that determined the victor? This is why I said the knights should get mics—
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: In any case! Whatever excuses you’ve got, it’s all too late now! I’m honored to announce the results of the first match of the day!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob

attributes.content: The winner—Maria Nearl!
attributes.name: Greatmouth Mob
